EAGE Members&#xd;
The European Association of Geoscientists and Engineers (EAGE) has currently 18.870 members (October 2015). EAGE publishes the number of its member on its montly magazine "First Break" in the hard copy and lists the new members on electronic version of the magazine.&#xd;
