EAGE Associated Societies&#xd;
The European Association of Geoscientists and Engineers (EAGE) has the Associated Society Membership and there are currently 59 Associated Societies. Through this membership local and national geoscientific societies are given the opportunity to use the knowledge and network of an international, professional society like EAGE.&#xd;
